						 <p>The idea here is nice and surreal and I enjoyed it up until the interviews, but unfortunately I found the tone of the Foundation guy in both logs to be massively unprofessional. That combined with the releasing of a person with anomalous abilities or under anomalous effects immediately after the interview, <em>to the police???</em> kind of ruined a good setup for me.</p> 
